{"tid":833974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共熱炒「瑞典辱華」 遊客訪俄受辱求助卻遭刪號","createTime":"2018-09-24T01:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T05:45:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":153,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"0432ec732deb5bd0df176a40bf7a8b6232439444","tid":833974,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2018/9-23/p9046501a806389347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2018%2F9-23%2Fp9046501a806389347.jpg&h=990f23ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共官方熱炒的所謂「瑞典辱華案」，雖然中國遊客無理取鬧、佔便宜碰瓷的內幕不斷被揭，北京依然緊抓不放，藉機批評「瑞典人權」。但日前中國遊客因為在俄羅斯遭長期欺凌而向官方求助，結果卻遭刪貼封號。<br />\n<br />\n9月16日，有中國女遊客在大陸社交媒體發文，抗議俄國人長年刻意欺凌、勒索中國遊客的惡行。文中稱，她日前跟團赴俄國旅行，搭乘火車時發現乘務員專挑中國人強收小費，而旅行社導遊解釋，這是俄國針對中國遊客的「不成文規定」。<br />\n<br />\n該遊客大呼不公，希望中共黨媒給討個說法。一些「愛國」網民紛紛跟帖「犯我中華！雖遠必誅！」，並主動標記中共駐俄大使館和中共黨媒。<br />\n<br />\n不過，幾天後，不僅這篇文章遭刪除，連該女陸客的帳號也「被消失」。<br />\n<br />\n許多支持她的網友都十分失望：「說好的戰狼外交呢？」<br />\n<br />\n還有一些曾力挺該文的網絡五毛則急忙改口：「當年拿了俄國那麽多錢推翻蔣介石，現在還錢不該嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n該女遊客發文，顯然是受中共官方緊追「瑞典辱華案」啟發。而中共官方對這兩件事的處理手法迥然不同，顯然是出於中共「外交戰略」的需要。<br />\n<br />\n北京面臨中美貿易戰高壓，俄羅斯是中共極力拉攏的對象。而瑞典則因為公開批評中國人權狀況，遭北京敵視。<br />\n<br />\n9月2日凌晨，中國遊客曾某一家因為提前抵達瑞典旅館，要求在大廳過夜遭拒後鬧場，遭警察驅出旅館後，依然在街上裝病博同情、假摔哭鬧，又被強制抬上警車拉走。<br />\n<br />\n該事件被中共黨媒炒作成「辱華事件」。官方藉機向瑞典「抗議」，批評「瑞典人權」。<br />\n<br />\n但知情網友紛紛披露，曾某一家為省錢有意「蹭過夜」，還讓老婆裝成女留學生一起「蹭房間」，遭旅館識破後惱羞成怒，因而撒潑大鬧。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典華人隨後在美媒發聲，批評中國遊客的無理舉動令當地華人非常丟臉，快「活不下去」了，要求媒體盡快公佈當地華人的意見和立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2018/09/23/a1392678.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2Fa1392678.html&d=6IMoQAHszAEhGvitxER%2F4AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e059651a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2018/09/23/a1392678.html</a>"},{"pid":"84f3bbbcc616331131e6f49f2eb8091401fb81fe","tid":833974,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d64c72d0e87bddcc56286ac36bbb05d3c64f990","tid":833974,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:51:26.000Z","msg":"好7<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de64802a3f1b92e822e4d341e7020b227c191eb","tid":833974,"uid":187076,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/095233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F095233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d8e6499c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3240c6adae5c366922b9375cf03a4650ed687fc6","tid":833974,"uid":31237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:53:22.000Z","msg":"欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"95f0e143a89c6caae2a0562e1ebd3a9742a1691e","tid":833974,"uid":4525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"契弟中國點敢出聲"},{"pid":"877fd0ec3496c8730d2c3d90a448ab253eb638c3","tid":833974,"uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/JUC0UHHF89rQM3OtVk0HTXRVRfLc9dbetyKpZ0A6m_Gja6MBQgm1G4OKhCOi27Cye92UWp35XoyjNeQp7A9wvYV3J_AeDSBiVuMpydTvrGVxgClBvoPj1PitgAWBcebCgYP_HICxzS3tGUlafY7dXbJDTaGcY5ibBm0q7Lh0J8GZsU-ye0wgEpuBeqSjxo0IjuKgBYNfnfbWREl8lGDhDTvFgMe-8el2NBcASiRdo_wbTIU0zHbZfp1-4ffyB1paj7NZuALdweT4xTTI__mM3BRU6ziyGRe7U2u5ELHJ8ULPpBgQwL7SGkdkFKkXMZazFqPNEGMHDCQPc_gjxHa12-Ep8SpnUvCQ9Y8Ab0OkuonAWU-TNU2Qq7MVmh2g0Bj2TPyUUU8QEfa6PyR3sGbx0hVu-_uOycvWNjtZ1LNJLThxO5Wz2phXf-TJNXc7CFY6gf7WME26A6vpSx3yywoUDcdtRrJd8vFnlRoWk3VUOqM_hBBX0W7_-DI